content:
One day, 
When I die,
No one offers me flowers! 
If I do not have them 
In my life, 
I do not need them 
In my grave!,pic.twitter.com/6eikEfBfkK
本物のブラック,ローズ, 実際にあるのですか,　初めて見ました。すご～い,
The genuine black rose originates from Halfeti on the Euphrates River in Turkey! It is the only place where it exists spontaneously! ,pic.twitter.com/YLs9vJ5W5R
Do not thank me! Thank Mother Nature and the Universe!
